Information & Download links: http://modules.sourceforge.net

Draco Developers:

Setup for CCS LAN:
1. check out Draco/environment from CVS.
2. from ~/.bashrc, source Draco/environment/bashrc/.bashrc.  This will 
   initialize the module system and load a default set of modules.

Setup for HPC:
1. check out Draco/environment from CVS (or use a copy from 
   /usr/projects/draco/...)
2. Make draco modules available to the already loaded module system:
   module use ~/draco/environment/Modules/hpc
   module use ~/draco/environment/Modules/[ct|rr-dev|tu|yr]-fe

Use:
% module avail
% module list
% module unload <name>
% module load <name>
% module switch <name1> <name2>
% module purge


